<sect2>
<title>Installation of <application>gnome-applets</application></title>

<para>Install <application>gnome-applets</application> by running the following commands:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=$GNOME_PREFIX --libexecdir=$GNOME_PREFIX/sbin \
--localstatedir=/var/lib --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

